License:	BSD-2-Clause/CC-BY-3.0/CC0-1.0/LGPL-3.0-or-later
Group:		X11/Applications/Sound
Source0:	https://download.kde.org/stable/plasma/%{kdeplasmaver}/%{kpname}-%{version}.tar.xz
